- Sections auto-filled: Project Overview (name + description from package.json/README), Tech Stack (detected from dependencies), Architecture Overview (monorepo packages with paths/types, or top-level dirs for single-package repos), Key Dependencies (extracted from detection), Git info (remote URL + default branch)
- Sections with clear TODO placeholder markers: Product Goals, Target Users, Key Workflows, Constraints & Non-Goals, Open Questions

**`apps/server/src/routes/setup/routes/project.ts`** (58 lines added):
- Step 3d in the project setup flow: generates spec.md in the project root
- Never overwrites existing spec.md (guarded by `fs.access` check)
- Reads description from `package.json` first, falls back to README first paragraph
- Only generates spec.md when `research` data is present (requires prior repo research)

